### **Components Addressed:**

**1. controller_board_v3 (URGENT: 2.1 weeks cover)**
- ✅ **Recommended Award:** Helix Microsystems — 10,000 units @ $39.80/unit = 
**$398,000**
- **Lead time:** 6 weeks; proven reliability (99.4% on-time, 0.2% defect rate 
since 2021)
- **Rationale:** Locks pricing against +6% inflationary trend; maintains 
flexibility (no exclusivity); avoids counterparty and lock-in risk
- **Status:** COMMITTED, pending HITL approval for $398k value

**⚠️ Meridian Exclusive Proposal (Escalated for Human Review)**
