performance gates (98%+ on-time, zero critical defects), 24-month extension @ 
$31/unit conditional on gate achievement
- **Action:** Awaiting human decision on counter-offer strategy (pilot-gate, 
modified exclusive, or outright rejection)

**2. harness_assembly_a (HIGH PRIORITY: 3.0 weeks cover)**
